OL,3,CPrison population spikes to record
OL,4,Chighs in England and Wales
OL,6,FThe number of people in English and
OL,7,FWelsh prisons has hit a record high,
OL,8,Fwith the number spiking by close to a
OL,9,Fthousand more inmates in the past
OL,10,Fmonth.
OL,12,FAs of August 30, some 88,350 people
OL,13,Fwere in prison, according to the
OL,14,FMinistry of Justice.
OL,16,FThat figure is up 988 people from just
OL,17,Ffour weeks ago on August 2. It is the
OL,18,Fhighest end-of-week figure since
OL,19,Fweekly population data was first
OL,20,Fpublished in 2011.
