OL,3,CPrison population spikes to record
OL,4,Chighs in England and Wales
OL,6,FIt also surpasses the highest total
OL,7,Fever recorded, which was 88,336 at end
OL,8,Fthe February 2024, based on separate
OL,9,Ffigures for the end-of-month
OL,10,Fpopulation size.
OL,12,FThe sharp rise in recent weeks is
OL,13,Flikely to have been driven by the
OL,14,Fnumber of jail sentences handed to
OL,15,Fpeople found guilty of taking part in
OL,16,Fthe recent disorder across parts of
OL,17,Fthe country.
