OL,3,CPrison population spikes to record
OL,4,Chighs in England and Wales
OL,6,FThe prison population in England and
OL,7,FWales has been rising for much of the
OL,8,Fpast three years, having dropped as
OL,9,Flow as 77,727 in April 2021 during the
OL,10,FCovid pandemic.
OL,12,FBefore the pandemic, the figure had
OL,13,Fbeen above 80,000 since December 2006.
OL,15,FIn the aftermath of the summer 2011
OL,16,Friots, the number climbed as high as
OL,17,F88,179 on December 2 2011, before
OL,18,Ffalling back in subsequent months.
