OL,3,CPrison population spikes to record
OL,4,Chighs in England and Wales
OL,6,FSteve Gillan, general secretary at the
OL,7,FPrison Officers' Association (POA)
OL,8,Fsaid: "The POA have been warning for
OL,9,Fseveral years that there is a crisis
OL,10,Fwithin our prisons and criminal
OL,11,Fjustice system, this has not occurred
OL,12,Fovernight.
OL,14,F"The neglect in funding and
OL,15,Fmismanagement by the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment over the last 14 years of
OL,17,Four prisons has come home to roost.
