OL,3,CPrison population spikes to record
OL,4,Chighs in England and Wales
OL,6,F"Perhaps now rather than just tinker
OL,7,Fwith prisons we will have a short-
OL,8,Fterm, medium and long-term plan by the
OL,9,FLabour government to ensure the
OL,10,Fgeneral public are never placed in
OL,11,Fthis position again."
OL,13,FThe data comes ahead of a scheme that
OL,14,Fwill see prisoners being freed early
OL,15,Fin response to the overcrowding crisis
OL,16,Fin England and Wales.
OL,18,FAn estimated 5,500 offenders are
OL,19,Fexpected to be released earlier than
OL,20,Fwas planned in the coming weeks under
OL,21,Fthe temporary measures.
