OL,6,FThese measures will not apply to those
OL,7,Fconvicted of sex offences, terrorism,
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse or some violent
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FThe government has said that those who
OL,12,Fare released will serve the rest of
OL,13,Ftheir sentence under strict licensing
OL,14,Fconditions.
