OL,6,FSpeaking to journalists while on a
OL,7,Ftrip to Berlin earlier this week,
OL,8,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,9,Fthat more prisons will be built in
OL,10,Fresponse to overcrowding once the
OL,11,Fgovernment has got its "hands on the
OL,12,Fplanning laws".
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, the prime minister said:
OL,15,F"We've got to change the planning
OL,16,Fregulation so we can build the prisons
OL,17,Fwe need, because they're taking far
OL,18,Ftoo long, it's far too slow, and
OL,19,Fthat's amongst the reasons we're in
OL,20,Fthe position we are.
